Don't ever stick you Galaxy Note 5 stylus in backward (which is surprisingly easy to do!) - you'll probably break S Pen detection on your phone, permanently.

Full article on flaw here: http://www.androidpolice.com/2015/08/25/video-probable-note-5-design-flaw-can-cause-s-pen-to-break-pen-detection-when-inserted-backward-or-get-hopelessly-stuck/

